code: @Override public void install(String coordinates) {     try {         FileUtils.writeStringToFile(repository, coordinates + "\n", true).     } catch (IOException e) {         throw new IOError(e).     } }
@Override public List<String> listPatches() {     try {         return IOUtils.readLines(new FileReader(repository)).     } catch (IOException e) {         throw new IOError(e).     } }
@Override public void clear() {     try {         repository.delete().         repository.createNewFile().     } catch (IOException e) {         throw new IOError(e).     } }
